verbose_text: The mRNA expression of AMFR was significantly decreased in the THP-1 cells transfected with AMFR siRNA for 24, 48, 72 and 96 h, compared with those transfected with scrambled siRNA (P < 0.05), and the lowest expression level of mRNA was measured at 72 h post-transfection with AMFR siRNA (XREF_FIG).
